===Noun===
'''loxodrome'''
#{{mathematics}} a [[line]] on a [[surface]] (such as the [[Earth]]) that cuts all [[meridian]]s at a constant [[angle]] (but not a [[right angle]])
# the [[path]] followed by a [[ship]] or [[aircraft]] that maintains a [[constant]] [[course]] by the [[compass]]
